				<div class="entry">

					<h2><a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/2012/09/10/jeremy-scahill-takes-down-msnbc-panel-on-obama-foreign-policy/">Jeremy Scahill Takes Down MSNBC Panel On Obama Foreign&nbsp;Policy</a></h2>

					<div class="post-info">
						<p>
							<span class="time">September 10, 2012</span>
															<span class="author">by <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/author/mktgeistmike/" title="Posts by mktgeistmike" rel="author">mktgeistmike</a></span>
