							<span class="time">September 7, 2012</span>
															<span class="author">by <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/author/mktgeistmike/" title="Posts by mktgeistmike" rel="author">mktgeistmike</a></span>
																						<span class="post-comments"><a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/2012/09/07/reality-check-1-on-1-with-president-obama-how-does-he-justify-a-kill-list/#respond" title="Comment on Reality Check: 1 on 1 With President Obama, How Does He Justify A Kill&nbsp;List?">Leave a comment</a></span>
